Legal Counsel, Global Healthcare MNC, Singapore – 3+ years PQE
Location:  Singapore
This is a great opportunity for a dynamic lawyer looking for an in-house role with an established MNC. As part of the regional legal team, the successful candidate will be based in Singapore and enjoy a full range of responsibilities providing legal support for our client's business operations in the APAC region.
Ideal candidates should have at least 3 years of good corporate commercial experience gained in a leading firm or in-house with a large corporate. Prior experience in the area of Healthcare and/or Life Science not necessary but advantageous.
